<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
January 9, 1994, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Book Review; Page 2; Book Review Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
