<TEXT>
<P>
 Why while away the hours listening to the latest tape-recorded best seller 
when you could be learning to speak Tibetan? 
</P>
<P>
 A three-volume, 18-cassette set, "Fluent Tibetan: A Proficiency Oriented 
Learning System," is new from the University of Virginia and an 11-member team 
of Tibetan-studies scholars, graduate students and native speakers. 
</P>
