</P>
<P>
 Laguna Hills 4, Laguna Beach 0 -- Nicole Restivo scored two goals and Sarah 
Lang had four saves for her 10th shutout for Laguna Hills (10-3-3, 1-0). 
</P>
<P>
 Costa Mesa 1, Estancia 1 -- Tesea Brown scored for Costa Mesa (5-1-3) and 
Tracie Manz for Estancia (6-4-3). 
</P>
<P>
 In the Estancia wrestling tournament: 
</P>
<P>
 Irvine wins -- Eight Irvine wrestlers finished with medals to lead Irvine 
(163) to the tournament championship. Baldwin Park finished second with 148 
points. 
</P>
<P>
