 In the Orange County Invitational field hockey tournament: 
</P>
<P>
 Edison earns top seeding -- Edison took the top spot for next weekend's 
quarterfinals by defeating Bonita, 3-1, Marina, 1-0, and host Fountain Valley, 
1-0. Jennifer Craig had two goals for Edison, and Lara Lundquist made eight 
saves. 
</P>
