COMMUNITY NEWS: SOUTHWEST: CRENSHAW; BLACK ARTISTS' GROUP BEGINS ITS 20TH YEAR 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 International Black Writers and Artists is beginning its 20th year with an 
open reading and art display from 3 to 5 p.m. today in the Community Room at 
the Baldwin Hills Crenshaw Plaza. 
</P>
