<DOCID> 002574 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
January 9, 1994, Sunday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 1; Column 4; Metro Desk 
