<HEADLINE>
<P>
20 SAILORS DIE IN WRECK 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 At least 20 young sailors were killed when the pickup truck they were in 
collided with a 10-wheel truck in Chonburi province south of Bangkok, 
newspapers said Saturday. 
</P>
