<DOCNO> LA010994-0364 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 002620 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
January 9, 1994, Sunday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Business; Part D; Page 1; Column 4; Financial Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
