COMMUNITY NEWS: SOUTHWEST: CRENSHAW; EVENTS TO CELEBRATE KING'S BIRTHDAY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The Southern Christian Leadership Conference and the Martin Luther King Jr. 
Legacy Assn. are sponsoring a week of activities celebrating the birthday of 
the Rev. Martin Luther King Jr.All events are open to the public. 
</P>
