<HEADLINE>
<P>
FOUL FOWL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 * The other day on the beach, I observed a gull-like bird spouting foul 
(fowl?) language. Could this have been a Howard's tern?  
</P>
<P>
