<P>
 Las Flores Canyon -- A story on Thursday concerning plans for a study of 
remedies to natural hazards in Las Flores Canyon incorrectly stated the 
proposed study would be on Malibu City Council's agenda Tuesday. It will be 
discussed at the council's regular Monday meeting. 
</P>
</TEXT>
